15 WHEREAS, Shawty Lo passed away on September 21, 2016, leaving a legacy of innovative,
16 influential, and authentic contributions to the hip hop community; and
17 WHEREAS, on March 22, 2025, Shawty Lo would have celebrated his 49th birthday.
18 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
19 recognize and commend Carlos Rico Walker for his significant impact on music and culture
20 in Atlanta as well as join in the celebration of his 49th birthday.
21 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
22 to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the public and the
23 press.
